Print summary for classcodes object

Source: R/summary.classcodes.R
print.summary.classcodes.Rd

Print summary for classcodes object

# S3 method for summary.classcodes
print(x, n_print = 50, ...)

Arguments

x

object of class summary.classcodes
n_print

maximum characters to print from the codes column
...

ignored

Value

Nothing. This function is called for its side effects

See also

Other classcodes: all_classcodes(), as.data.frame.classified(), classcodes, set_classcodes(), summary.classcodes(), visualize()

Examples

print(summary(elixhauser, coding = "icd10cm"))
